node.text: When the 🌕 hits your 👀 like a big…..tortilla pizza? I mean that isn’t quite right, but this pizza definitely is. Should I be concerned that a cookie basically turns into a cake? Yes I should be. Do I care? No.

🎶: @mariachi_teocuitatlan

node.text: You think you know someone, but have you ever spent an afternoon at their own personal sanctuary? I mean I have obviously spent time at the pad of @chadwoodinteriors but you may not have. Let’s change that.  From flea market finds to flowers cut (read: stolen) from his neighbor's yard, check out today’s video to see where this eclectic Chad of All Trades spends his downtime.

node.text: You’ve been getting a lot of @chadwoodhair and I lately, in all our many forms - home decor, making food, serving drinks (and lewks) - so we thought it’s only fair to give you the chance to ask all your most burning questions. Watch today’s IGTV to hear about my favorite emoji, our favorite snack and our biggest pet peeves about the other 🦄🧃
